patthana15.23:1.1_0: Sahetukaṁ kusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasahetuko nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.23:2.1_0: Sahetukaṁ akusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasahetuko naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …. Hetuyā tīṇi,
patthana15.23:3.1_0: Ahetukaṁ abyākataṁ dhammaṁ paccayā naahetuko naabyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuyā ekaṁ, ārammaṇe tīṇi,
